# Baca isi data.yaml
with open('data.yaml', 'r') as f:
    lines = f.readlines()

# Edit baris train, val, test
for i, line in enumerate(lines):
    if line.startswith('train:'):
        lines[i] = 'train: train/images\n'
    elif line.startswith('val:'):
        lines[i] = 'val: valid/images\n'
    elif line.startswith('test:'):
        lines[i] = 'test: test/images\n'

# Tulis ulang ke file data.yaml
with open('data.yaml', 'w') as f:
    f.writelines(lines)

print("data.yaml berhasil diperbarui:")
with open('data.yaml', 'r') as f:
    print(f.read())

from PIL import Image
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

# Buka gambar asli
img = Image.open('image_1_127_jpg.rf.00427966330d7aa33b0fc23041eef76d.jpg')
img_flip = img.transpose(Image.FLIP_LEFT_RIGHT)
img_rot = img.rotate(15)

# Tampilkan semua gambar
plt.figure(figsize=(12, 4))

plt.subplot(1, 3, 1)
plt.imshow(img)
plt.title("Asli")
plt.axis('off')

plt.subplot(1, 3, 2)
plt.imshow(img_flip)
plt.title("Flip")
plt.axis('off')

plt.subplot(1, 3, 3)
plt.imshow(img_rot)
plt.title("Rotate 15°")
plt.axis('off')

plt.show()

# Konversi ke array jika perlu
img_np = np.array(img)
img_flip_np = np.array(img_flip)
img_rot_np = np.array(img_rot)

# Lakukan prediksi
res1 = model.predict(source=img_np)
res2 = model.predict(source=img_flip_np)
res3 = model.predict(source=img_rot_np)

# Kombinasikan hasil prediksi di sini sesuai kebutuhan
# Misalnya: voting klasifikasi, gabung bounding box, dst
